{"tid":538103,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"純潔的少女感與成熟的女性感並存,非常稀有的存在","createTime":"2018-01-23T10:09:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-28T10:10:36.000Z","uid":3806,"like":8,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"ced09f53c9106e95cf84c560177ea3412e40c299","tid":538103,"uid":3806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T10:09:40.000Z","msg":"音樂劇「アメリ」（天使愛美麗）初主演決定 ！<br />\n麻友表示「被告知要主演百老匯上演的作品的主角時，目瞪口呆得感到很驚訝。同時交雜著開心和不安的心情湧上來，又是興奮又是消沈的，但既然被選中了，我會拼盡現在的我的所有，全身心得投入其中的。」<br />\n電影版在日本突破16億日元，去年4月開始在百老匯音樂劇化。日本版的導演由元寶塚歌劇団導演児玉明子擔任，並表示「<span style=\"color: red;\">（渡辺）是純潔的少女感與成熟的女性感並存非常稀有的存在</span>。在日本沒有比這更合適的卡司了。」[作揖]<br />\n日程<br />\n5/18～6/3東京・天王洲銀河劇場　<br />\n6/7～6/10大阪・森ノ宮ピロティホール<br />\n（天使愛美麗大家都知道，就不介紹了，再次感謝感激🙏🙏)<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/23/180825_6d7567b67a2bf4ad20397cf2d1210fe1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F23%2F180825_6d7567b67a2bf4ad20397cf2d1210fe1.png&h=946b48cc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d2fe1d84a233f3d485eede6063b28bbd73ad9ee7","tid":538103,"uid":60092,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T10:10:29.000Z","msg":"G"},{"pid":"f021647be0995be38509328f9d0714583c9af9ae","tid":538103,"uid":3806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T10:10:55.000Z","msg":"麻友已經昇華到另一階段了😭👍🏻"},{"pid":"a81cff64507fa4a02091a1b8b3aeba8256e67299","tid":538103,"uid":3806,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d2fe1d84a233f3d485eede6063b28bbd73ad9ee7","tid":538103,"uid":60092,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T10:10:29.000Z","msg":"G"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T10:11:07.000Z","msg":"𨳒你老母親節"},{"pid":"2d43b0ae9e596d6cb237aeea2ae8cd2d9abca48e","tid":538103,"uid":99364,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T10:11:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ec4fadc113a3ac5599fcd77e14f51660371ecd6b","tid":538103,"uid":43979,"like":0,"dis